## File References

Rules use the `[filename](mdc:filename)` syntax to reference files:
- Links are relative to workspace root
- Clicking opens the file in Cursor
- Helps navigate codebase quickly

Example:
```markdown
See [src/components/thread/markdown-text.tsx](mdc:src/components/thread/markdown-text.tsx)
```

